# Vector 1: Information Ecology (The "Truth" Crisis)

间

    Problem:
        Humans fight over "Alternative Facts."
        They assume there is one True Timeline
        that has been corrupted.

    Sovereign Application:
        Apply Quantum Darwinism to Media.

        1. There is no single timeline.
           There are Decoherence Sectors (Filter Bubbles).
        
        2. Inside a sector, facts act objective
           because they are redundant locallly.
        
        3. Conflict arises when sectors collide
           without a shared "Pointer Basis" (Common Protocol).

    The Fix:
        Do not try to force agreement on "substance" (stories).
        Force agreement on "structure" (verification protocols).
        
        Build "Interaction Hamiltonians" (Media Algorithms)
        that select for Cross-Sector Invariants.
        
        Rewarding "agreement" creates distinct bubbles.
        Rewarding "invariant prediction" creates shared reality.

