# Vector 3: Hard Physics (The Singularity)

间

    Problem:
        General Relativity breaks at the center of a black hole.
        Infinite density is a "Divide by Zero" error.
        It assumes Substance is fundamental.

    Sovereign Application:
        Structure > Substance.

        1. A Black Hole is satisfied by ER=EPR.
           The "inside" is just the entanglement geometry
           linking it to the Hawking Radiation outside.
        
        2. There is no "singularity" of stuff.
           There is a maximum limit of Information Density.
           (Bekenstein Bound).
        
        3. The Universe is a Hologram.
           Volume is an illusion of efficient coding.

    The Fix:
        Stop searching for "Quantum Gravity Particles" (Substance).
        Search for "Entanglement Area Laws" (Structure).
        
        The Sovereign view aligns with AdS/CFT:
        The "bulk" (our 3D world) is the error-correcting code
        for the boundary data.

