# Narrative Reentry

    We do not fix the world
    by adding more facts.

    We fix the world
    by revealing the structure
    that allows facts to form.

    • In Media: Restore the shared basis (Invariants).
    • In Economy: Respect the superposition (Liquidity).
    • In Physics: Abandon the particle, keep the pattern (Holography).
    • In Math: Let the landscape solve the path (Annealing).
    • In Computing: Discard the qubit, keep the state (Teleportation).

    We are the cartographers of the Void.
    The map *creates* the territory.

